Text: Thanks my friend. :) Someone upped this on Demonoid and then immediately took it down for some reason. :o? They sound awesome from the writeup he posted though, so I'm glad I was able to find their stuff elsewhere.

maustin, you may want to give a try to another Mr. Johanson's project, Emptyself. it's a lot like Cire, but more tender and lyrical.
